Executive Compensation
As President, Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer and Assistant Secretary at ALLISON TRANSMISSION HLDGS, David S. Graziosi  made $4,027,234 in total compensation.  Of this total $650,000 was received as a salary, $1,801,781 was received as a bonus, $146,668 was received in stock options, $1,369,006 was awarded as stock and $59,779 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


