Insider Activity


Individual




David S. Graziosi



Mr. David S. Graziosi is President & Chief Financial Officer at Allison Transmission Holdings, Inc. and President, Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer at Allison Transmission, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Fallbrook Technologies, Inc. Mr. Graziosi was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Covalence Specialty Materials Corp., Vice President-Finance Precursors & Epoxy Resins by Momentive Specialty Chemicals, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by HSC Capital Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Resolution Performance Products LLC, a Principal by Colgate-Palmolive Co., Finance Director by GenTek, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Business Controller by Reheis, Inc., Director-Internal Audit & Assistant Controller by Sun Chemical Group BV, and Chief Financial Officer & Vice President by Tata Chemicals North America, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from The State University of New York and an MBA from Rutgers State University of New Jersey.



